{"tid":2057231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人的日程表","createTime":"2020-06-09T08:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T06:58:48.000Z","uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de5f3aecda767aa1e7687f51bb54075bf561e7b9","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"朝早到龍門冰室食早餐<br />\n當然要食龍門招牌早餐<br />\n豬扒公仔麵啦<br />\n<br />\n食完早餐去返工<br />\n搭車過程中<br />\n當然高呼<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n香港人反抗香港獨立等口號<br />\n<br />\n中午放飯時<br />\n到龍門冰室享用黃到無得再黃既<br />\n龍門咖喱牛腩飯<br />\n<br />\n食完lunch<br />\n夠鐘睇蕭生既片<br />\n睇完再comment like share<br />\n<br />\n收工之後<br />\n當然約埋同事去商場<br />\n唱願光歸香港<br />\n畫面幾靚<br />\n然後情不自禁下打卡po ig<br />\n<br />\n唱完歌<br />\n梗係要到煲底<br />\n同朋友一齊打邊爐<br />\n走之前再係連儂牆前影相<br />\n大叫五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n回家後<br />\n翻看城寨節目<br />\n聽劉細良教我地下一步點做<br />\n邊d人係鬼偽民主派<br />\n<br />\n臨瞓前<br />\n上熱狗page上連登屌熱狗<br />\n再係ig story po 好嬲警暴好嬲嗰政府<br />\n<br />\n啊～咁就完左美好既一日"},{"pid":"5be5498c2c87091bf51ac4d5194fd08922cff441","tid":2057231,"uid":63822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 多蒙特全隊空難</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">洗白黑警</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmkQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmkQT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmfaT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmfaT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「歷史回顧，無忘初心」</div><pre><code data-type=\"\">2019年7月17日\n717銀髮族大遊行</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRy0DgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRy0DgX.jpg&h=0bd37cda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8dc36903fc8fcb9f25c26690c3141b9993aa34","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"日程表唔係唔推嘛"},{"pid":"df8d43f999d13390c8a66590fbe4d78c0b3e8a03","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cca3666d309ca8a00b43674453d9d4f1dc2cb1e","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cb51b11634b2c0e26d9b1929568fcd66a399b6f","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b825166cb50a7b1a7c6ff54ff36bf17f439a19c5","tid":2057231,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"咁都上唔到熱門<br />\n係味想輸"},{"pid":"32136eb0ecd4b05502ff08c4e5bc353344c4388a","tid":2057231,"uid":60155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 又改名 又出五毛POST<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9040cd1610938b0e79246ae672507524957f60c6","tid":2057231,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"起底：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/60916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih